            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-10365310",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Authentication Bypass Using an Alternate Path or Channel vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2025-49125) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-tomcat@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6\n# Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Authentication Bypass Using an Alternate Path or Channel due to how `PreResources` or `PostResources` handle pre-resources or post-resources mounted at non-root locations. An attacker can gain unauthorized access to protected resources by crafting requests to unexpected paths that bypass intended security constraints.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.106, 10.1.42, 11.0.8 or higher.\n# References\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-11.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Thread](https://lists.apache.org/thread/m66cytbfrty9k7dc4cg6tl1czhsnbywk)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/7617b9c247bc77ed0444dd69adcd8aa48777886c)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/9418e3ff9f1f4c006b4661311ae9376c52d162b9)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/d94bd36fb7eb32e790dae0339bc249069649a637)\n"
              },
