            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-1061939",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Information Disclosure vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2021-24122) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-tomcat@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6\n# Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Information Disclosure. When serving resources from a network location using the NTFS file system, affected versions were susceptible to JSP source code disclosure in some configurations. The root cause was the unexpected behaviour of the JRE API `File.getCanonicalPath()` which in turn was caused by the inconsistent behaviour of the Windows API (FindFirstFileW) in some circumstances.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 10.0.0-M10, 9.0.40, 8.5.60, 7.0.107 or higher.\n# References\n- [Apache Security Advisory](https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/r1595889b083e05986f42b944dc43060d6b083022260b6ea64d2cec52%40%3Cannounce.tomcat.apache.org%3E)\n- [Apache Tomcat 10.x Advisories](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat 7.x Advisories](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-7.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat 8.x Advisories](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-8.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat 9.x Advisories](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/7f004ac4531c45f9a2a2d1470561fe135cf27bc2)\n"
              },
              "properties": {
                "tags": [
                  "security",
                  "CWE-200",
                  "maven"
                ],
                "cvssv3_baseScore": 5.3,
                "security-severity": "5.3"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-1080637",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "High severity - Remote Code Execution (RCE) vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2021-25329) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-tomcat@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6\n# Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Remote Code Execution (RCE). The fix for CVE-2020-9484 was incomplete. When using Apache Tomcat with a configuration edge case that was highly unlikely to be used, the Tomcat instance was still vulnerable to CVE-2020-9494. Note that both the previously published prerequisites for CVE-2020-9484 and the previously published mitigations for CVE-2020-9484 also apply to this issue.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 10.0.2, 9.0.43, 8.5.63, 7.0.108 or higher.\n# References\n- [Apache Security Advisory](https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/rfe62fbf9d4c314f166fe8c668e50e5d9dd882a99447f26f0367474bf%40%3Cannounce.tomcat.apache.org%3E)\n"
              },
              "properties": {
                "tags": [
                  "security",
                  "CWE-94",
                  "maven"
                ],
                "cvssv3_baseScore": 7,
                "security-severity": "7"
              }
