              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2026-29145) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-tomcat@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6\n# Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Improper Authentication in `processOCSPRequest()`, which is part of the the `CLIENT_CERT` authentication process. An attacker can trigger a soft-fail of OCSP checks when soft-fail is disabled.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.116, 10.1.53, 11.0.20 or higher.\n# References\n- [Apache Mailing List](https://lists.apache.org/thread/yz5fxmhd2j43wgqykssdo7kltws57jfz)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/721591f7bff424c693f26adc18ae9b9abac3655b)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat-native/commit/a0127f7d3b68dca553261f8d7d3540bfeeafc0d2)\n- [OSS Security Advisory](http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2026/04/09/23)\n"
