              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-16643276",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Timing Attack vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2026-43514) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-tomcat@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6\n# Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Timing Attack via AJP secret comparison. An attacker can determine whether a guessed secret is correct by measuring the time taken to compare secrets, potentially allowing unauthorized access through a timing side-channel attack.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 9.0.118, 10.1.55, 11.0.22 or higher.\n# References\n- [Apache Mailing List](https://lists.apache.org/thread/2k654v5cq123npfsd1b2kk1y30owqb1m)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/6771e06aee1e6da82b36d528a3f6a9969c682748)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/ebdce4eed4c2a7ba1334902973c4b320e414c481)\n"
              },
              "properties": {
