            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGAPACHETOMCATEMBED-6092281",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "High severity - Improper Input Validation vulnerability in org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2023-46589) org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-web@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-tomcat@1.4.3.RELEASE › org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core@8.5.6\n# Overview\n[org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core) is a Core Tomcat implementation.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Improper Input Validation due to the improper parsing of HTTP trailer headers. An attacker can manipulate the server into treating a single request as multiple requests by sending a trailer header that exceeds the header size limit. This could lead to request smuggling when the server is behind a reverse proxy.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core` to version 8.5.96, 9.0.83, 10.1.16, 11.0.0-M10 or higher.\n# References\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://lists.apache.org/thread/0rqq6ktozqc42ro8hhxdmmdjm1k1tpxr)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-10.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-11.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-8.html)\n- [Apache Tomcat Advisory](https://tomcat.apache.org/security-9.html)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/6f181e1062a472bc5f0234980f66cbde42c1041b)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/7a2d8818fcea0b51747a67af9510ce7977245ebd)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/aa92971e879a519384c517febc39fd04c48d4642)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/apache/tomcat/commit/b5776d769bffeade865061bc8ecbeb2b56167b08)\n"
              },
              "properties": {
