            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGSPRINGFRAMEWORK-5422217",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Allocation of Resources Without Limits or Throttling vulnerability in org.springframework:spring-expression"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2023-20863) org.springframework:spring-expression@4.3.5.RELEASE"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.springframework:spring-expression\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-security@1.2.0.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-security@1.2.0.RELEASE › org.springframework:spring-expression@4.3.5.RELEASE\n# Overview\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Allocation of Resources Without Limits or Throttling when a user provides a very long `SpEL` expression.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.springframework:spring-expression` to version 5.2.24.RELEASE, 5.3.27, 6.0.8 or higher.\n# References\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/commit/965a6392757d20f9db19241126fcc719a51eac15)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/commit/b73f5fcac22555f844cf27a7eeb876cb9d7f7f7e)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/commit/ebc82654282bda547fbc20a9749ab1bda886a46f)\n- [Vulnerability Advisory](https://spring.io/security/cve-2023-20863)\n"
