            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGSPRINGFRAMEWORKSECURITY-5950401",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Integer Overflow or Wraparound vulnerability in org.springframework.security:spring-security-core"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2022-22976) org.springframework.security:spring-security-core@4.1.4.RELEASE"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.springframework.security:spring-security-core\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-security@1.2.0.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-security@1.2.0.RELEASE › org.springframework.security:spring-security-config@4.1.4.RELEASE › org.springframework.security:spring-security-core@4.1.4.RELEASE\n# Overview\n[org.springframework.security:spring-security-core](http://spring.io/spring-security) is a package that provides security services for the Spring IO Platform.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Integer Overflow or Wraparound when using the BCrypt class with the maximum work factor (31). In such a case, the encoder does not perform any salt rounds due to the overflow.\r\n\r\n**Note:**\r\n\r\nThe default settings are not affected by this CVE.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.springframework.security:spring-security-core` to version 5.4.11 or higher.\n# References\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/commit/5f7fc0eb265f97fe720ec1ad6b4021001101a2a9)\n- [GitHub Fix Commit v5.5.7](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/commit/0bd7daf899305eac4b2b0a070db8f9536ac384c5)\n- [GitHub Fix Commit v5.6.4](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/commit/a40f73521c0dd88b879ff6165d280e78bdf8154f)\n- [VMware Tanzu Security Advisory](https://tanzu.vmware.com/security/cve-2022-22976)\n"
              },
              "properties": {
