            {
              "id": "SNYK-JAVA-ORGSPRINGFRAMEWORKSECURITY-474642",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Medium severity - Access Restriction Bypass vulnerability in org.springframework.security:spring-security-web"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "(CVE-2018-1199) org.springframework.security:spring-security-web@4.1.4.RELEASE"
              },
              "help": {
                "text": "",
                "markdown": "* Package Manager: maven\n* Vulnerable module: org.springframework.security:spring-security-web\n* Introduced through: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917, org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-security@1.2.0.RELEASE and others\n### Detailed paths\n* _Introduced through_: com.myapp:wezvatech-demo@9739110917 › org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-security@1.2.0.RELEASE › org.springframework.security:spring-security-web@4.1.4.RELEASE\n# Overview\n[org.springframework.security:spring-security-web](https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.springframework.security/spring-security-web) is a package within Spring Security that provides security services for the Spring IO Platform.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Access Restriction Bypass. It does not consider URL path parameters when processing security constraints. By adding a URL path parameter with special encodings, an attacker may be able to bypass a security constraint.\n# Remediation\nUpgrade `org.springframework.security:spring-security-web` to version 4.1.5.RELEASE, 4.2.4.RELEASE, 5.0.3.RELEASE or higher.\n# References\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/commit/0eef5b4b425ab42b9fa0fde1a3f36a37b92558f)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/commit/65da28e4bf62f58fb130ba727cbbd621b44a36d)\n- [GitHub Commit](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/commit/cb8041ba67635edafcc934498ef82707157fd22)\n- [Pivotal Security Report](https://pivotal.io/security/cve-2018-1199)\n"
              },
              "properties": {
